Package: lvsem
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Structural Equation Modeling with Latent Variable Scores
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("lvsem", "Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "example@example.com")
Description: Lightweight helpers for estimating structural equation models
    from latent variable scores. The package includes utilities for creating
    multi-block latent variable scores, estimating path coefficients, computing
    effects, bootstrapping structural paths, and summarizing reflective
    measurement blocks.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
